    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Orientation" kindref="compound">Orientation</ref> allows the user to determine the orientation of the device. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>A signal is emitted whenever the orientation changes. <ref refid="namespaceDali" kindref="compound">Dali</ref> applications have full control over visual layout when the device is rotated i.e. the application developer decides which UI controls to rotate, if any. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
